{"id": "1370489682239950919", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "首先 講解一下角色的定位、作用", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T19:56:42.713000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370491838925897898", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "克珀珊特是祝福型(奶媽)的喚醒體\n與其他同為祝福型(綠色)的喚醒體不同，克珀的血量最高有99滴，這足以面對一些隨機傷害，能在前排過早被擊破時承受一定傷害，更容易活到殘局，也能在殘局取得一定的優勢。", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:05:16.907000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370492279600578680", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "儘管如此，還是建議將其放置於隊伍的1、2號位置\n因為命輪、隊伍的一些配置", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:07:01.972000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-10T14:37:43.013000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370492382445047838", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:07:26.492000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1370492381895589888", "filename": "Screenshot_20250510_034234_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 240790, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1370489285458923520/1370492381895589888/Screenshot_20250510_034234_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cb80be&is=69ca2f3e&hm=783d0aeda53cfadd3aba2cc9b448deeb13d37593430a3e1a9e7640b1966bc8ea&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370494440065470485", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "狂氣\n克珀能使2名隊友獲得3層屏障，並讓溢出的屏障轉化為蓄力\n建議搭配上能獲得屏障的隊友，在第一次狂氣時獲得蓄力\n此外，在死鬥時使用有奇效\n因死鬥會減少屏障上限，所以一定會獲得蓄力", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:15:37.067000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370494484369903676", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:15:47.630000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1370494483719917751", "filename": "Screenshot_20250510_034238_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 242955, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1370489285458923520/1370494483719917751/Screenshot_20250510_034238_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cb82b3&is=69ca3133&hm=80082c8921795c79409f3f948795448c0f67867e094da48231cd469bb26eb686&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370495453317304384", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "其麻痺、遲緩效果十分優秀\n能與其他有麻痺的技能作配合\n一層的遲緩也為後續有再上遲緩的打算留有空間", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:19:38.645000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
