{"id": "1370496228701372578", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "強化及30狂氣 有助隊友快速開啟第一次狂氣\n配合一些有狂氣充能的隊友 也有不錯的效果", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:22:43.511000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
