{"id": "1370497280116789269", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然有預備\n不過 4算力的回血卡加上其他技能卡的算力消耗都比較多 使克珀有點笨重，算力消耗有點大", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:26:54.188000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-10T01:18:30.760000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370497440511295588", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:27:32.429000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1370497440188203058", "filename": "Screenshot_20250510_034254_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 205172, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1370489285458923520/1370497440188203058/Screenshot_20250510_034254_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cb8574&is=69ca33f4&hm=eb64b7ded2e8ea69f4a567b2d9355a38a001483ea74688cf803a2d265b6cb9a6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370500769396166928", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "命輪\n開局的好裝備\n配合克珀能打出奇效\n例如（狂氣對象為自己）\n狂氣前裝上能+1蓄力 狂氣後裝上能+30狂 較大機會能在新回合開始時再+30狂氣（3屏障比較難破）\n\n30狂氣很多 能使克珀回轉起來\n缺點是1屏障容易被破 不過克珀能使其變為3屏障 所以在第1次狂氣後 30狂氣的效果將較難丟失 也可以開始轉起來", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:40:46.097000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:41:28.386000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1370502070523920466", "channel_id": "1370489285458923520", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "克珀的殘局優勢\n1.血量較高\n2.有回血\n3.有回狂、強化\n4.能在自己有屏障的同時 使對方麻痺、遲緩\n令對方看著自己上屏障、蓄力、強化 而又無能為力", "timestamp": "2025-05-09T20:45:56.310000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1370489285458923520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單分享 領航員ー克珀珊特 及 命輪聖火中的指引 在相位對弈(PVP)中的作用、隊伍", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
